headline: Ex-Citigroup Asia Managing Director Shaw Sues Bank in Hong Kong
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Philip John Shaw, a former head of Pan-Asia Execution Services at Citigroup Inc., sued the US bank to contest his summary dismissal in March 2019, after other ex-sales traders filed similar claims with the city’s employment tribunal earlier this month.
